title: NetApp Filer: Snapvault/Snapmirror Lag-time
agents: netapp
catalog: hw/storagehw/netapp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_netapp) are deprecated
 and will be removed in a future version.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "NetApp via Ontap REST API" ruleset.

 The check monitors the lag-time of snapvault volumes.
 You can configure levels at which age the check should report {WARN} and {CRIT}.
 Per default the check is {OK}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each snapvault volume.

item:
 The volume name, e.g. /vol/ipb_datas/
